author: Mark Manson
description:
Most people use ChatGPT to write emails or book flights. In this video, I put AI to the test. Not as a productivity hack, but as a personal growth tool. You’ll see exactly how to structure prompts for maximum depth, how different models think, and how to turn AI into the ultimate self-improvement coach. 
   
Plus, I built 7 powerful AI prompts designed to change your life. Check out the link in the comments to download the free PDF👇
title: How to Use AI to Become a Better Person
